        <marginalia hand="English_secretary" anchor_text="&agrave; meo sensu post morte[m] ababfutura sunt, siue, vt sapientissimi homines putaueru[n]t, ad aliqua[m] animi mei partem pertinebunt">
            <language ident="LA">
                <position place="head" book_orientation="0">
                    <marginalia_text>
                        Quida[m] puta[n]t gloria[m] &amp; laudem nostraru[m] post mortem a sensu n[ost]ro abfutura Quidam ad aliquam animi partem pertinere putaueru[n]t
                    </marginalia_text>
                </position>
            </language>
            <translation>
                Certain people think that our glory and praise after their death will vanish from our senses. They thought that some part of the soul pertains.
            </translation>
        </marginalia>
        
